Our configuation scripts are not prepared to work for CP-examples 
with LCG library version of Tauola and TauSpinner. This is possible 
and reasonably straigtforward, but not necessarily very practical 
because of compiles/version dependencies for 
root, mc-tester, hepmc libraries.

The following aspects need to be kept in mind (detailed
instruction will be provided on the basis of pilot users experience):


